com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.user

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ami.mse.ucms.db.entities.user.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Entity
public class User
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Entity class that modeling the data base table User. Contains columns, relations to the other tables and queries that extract information from this table. The purpose of this table is to saves information for the different users that are registered in the system.
    Author:
    Tony
